#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for "Account name"</h2>
To use this software, you must login to the Brightsands software suite.
In most cases, you will be given an account (and privileges) on this system by
the software administrator, but in some cases you create the account yourself.
<p>Type in the account you are using or the account you wish to create.
Account names are <b>not</b> case sensitive.
